---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../../components/CTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Rotary Hearth Furnace Parts For Precision Heating" description="You need precise atmospheric sealing and thermal uniformity for rotary heating cycles. Our accessories maintain critical parameters through the entire rotation.">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-4">Furnace Application Solutions</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 mb-8 leading-tight">Rotary Hearth Furnace Parts For Precision Heating</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 mb-12">
        <p>You need precise atmospheric sealing and thermal uniformity as your parts move through the rotary heating cycle. Our specialized furnace accessories for rotary hearth systems are designed to maintain critical process parameters throughout the entire 360-degree rotation. You will find that our components reduce heat loss and improve carbon potential control, ensuring that every part in your batch meets the highest metallurgical standards.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Technical Challenge</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Rotary systems struggle with door sealing and maintaining consistent gas concentration as the table turns. You need dynamic sealing solutions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Weigu Solution</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Weigu provides advanced furnace gaskets and liquid drip systems for carburizing. You achieve superior atmospheric stability even in large rotary systems.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="bg-blue-900 text-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Key Components For This Application</h2>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> High-Temp Sealing Kits</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Precision Liquid Feeders</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Recorders & Sensors</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Custom Refractory Fixings</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="mt-16">
        <CTA title="Optimize Your Rotary Hearth Process Today" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
